==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Three-pile
<hw>Three"-pile`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An old name for
the finest and most costly kind of velvet, having a fine, thick
pile.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I have served Prince Florizel and in my time wore
<qex>three-pile</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Three-piled</ent>⟦br⟧
